Name: CarKour
About the game: CarKour is the first game dedicated to car parking games, and it is a great challenge for you to test your skill in controlling and driving the car to reach the happy ending. Contains many hints, marks and stickers that are there to help you pass the difficult obstacles Contains the feature of bending forward and backward during high jumps using the Q and E keys. Does not contain Check Points, so every loss is considered a start over Contains the main control keys for a car , inside and outside cameras , in addition to the car Respawn
